	<li><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><b><strong>Review Chnages Reason:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>{{{Site_Visit_Report__c.Negotation_Reason__c}}}</span></span></li>
</ul>

<div><br />
